The paper discusses steganography techniques in the context of VoIP, which involves network protocols and communication security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Additionally, the paper also involves multimedia communication (cs.MM), network infrastructure (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), and cybernetics (cs.CY).
